- We'd have to run left
at full speed.

759
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:03,333
What's your plan?
- Hmm.

760
00:34:03,666 --> 00:34:05,166
I could shove Rem toward you,

761
00:34:05,250 --> 00:34:07,125
