and briefly stare at you two,

762
00:34:07,208 --> 00:34:08,541
then run tragically
to the right.

763
00:34:08,625 --> 00:34:10,291
- So you wanna draw
the ulgarm's attention

764
00:34:10,375 --> 00:34:11,625
while I take Rem
and run to safety.

765
00:34:11,708 --> 00:34:13,250
- Could you not reduce
my heroic moment to such

766
00:34:13,333 --> 00:34:14,916
a simple plan?
- No, there's no way

767
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:16,333
you can survive on your own.

768
00:34:16,416 --> 00:34:19,083
I'm begging of you.
Please don't.

769
00:34:19,166 --> 00:34:20,500
You mustn't!

770
00:34:21,041 --> 00:34:22,625
- Don't go worrying about me.

771
00:34:22,708 --> 00:34:25,083
I have a brilliant idea
for rounding up

772
00:34:25,166 --> 00:34:26,458
all the mabeasts
you don't know about.

773
00:34:26,541 --> 00:34:27,916
- Subaru.

774
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:30,125
Why would you do all this?

775
00:34:30,875 --> 00:34:32,333
- Well, the thing is...

776
00:34:36,166 --> 00:34:39,791
You were my partner on the very
first date I ever went on.

777
00:34:39,875 --> 00:34:42,583
I could never be so heartless
that I'd abandon you.

778
00:34:42,666 --> 00:34:44,541
- [gasping]

779
00:34:46,625 --> 00:34:48,458
- Right, I guess
I'd better go ahead

780
00:34:48,541 --> 00:34:49,958
and get this thing going, then.

781
00:34:50,041 --> 00:34:51,166
Take care of Rem, okay?

782
00:34:51,250 --> 00:34:52,416
I'm counting on you!

783
00:34:52,500 --> 00:34:54,416
- I'll be praying
for our safe reunion, Barasu.

784
00:34:54,500 --> 00:34:56,208
- [grunts]

785
00:34:56,291 --> 00:34:58,666
- He's risking his life
to buy us some time.

786
00:34:58,750 --> 00:35:00,625
So let's make the most of it.

787
00:35:00,708 --> 00:35:02,333
- [breathing heavily]

788
00:35:02,416 --> 00:35:03,791
[snarling]

789
00:35:03,875 --> 00:35:05,708
[panting]

790
00:35:06,875 --> 00:35:08,791
<i>[Konomi Suzuki's "Redo"]</i>

791
00:35:08,875 --> 00:35:11,000
I'd love to finish you off
right about now,

792
00:35:11,083 --> 00:35:12,041
you little mutt.

793
00:35:12,125 --> 00:35:14,083
[snarling]

794
00:35:14,166 --> 00:35:17,416
<i>♪ ♪</i>

795
00:35:17,500 --> 00:35:20,416
