796
00:35:20,500 --> 00:35:22,625
<i>♪ ♪</i>

797
00:35:22,708 --> 00:35:24,166
- [grunts]
Yeah.

798
00:35:24,250 --> 00:35:25,833
I've got an ace up my sleeve,
too.

799
00:35:25,916 --> 00:35:27,583
It's you and me, pal.

800
00:35:27,666 --> 00:35:29,541
Hope you're ready.
[grunts]

801
00:35:29,625 --> 00:35:32,791
- Sister, Subaru's surrounded!
He's not going to--

802
00:35:32,875 --> 00:35:34,375
- Don't look back, Rem,

803
00:35:34,458 --> 00:35:37,000
or Barusu's determination
will be for nothing.

804
00:35:37,083 --> 00:35:38,458
- [gasps]

805
00:35:38,541 --> 00:35:41,458
<i>- [singing in Japanese]</i>

806
00:35:41,541 --> 00:35:43,125
<i>♪ ♪</i>

807
00:35:43,208 --> 00:35:44,791
- [gasping]

808
00:35:44,875 --> 00:35:46,208
Sissy, please!

809
00:35:46,291 --> 00:35:47,958
- [gasps]

810
00:35:48,041 --> 00:35:50,958
<i>- [singing in Japanese]</i>

811
00:35:51,041 --> 00:35:53,000
<i>♪ ♪</i>

812
00:35:53,083 --> 00:35:54,208
- [gasps]

813
00:35:54,291 --> 00:35:56,708
Subaru!

814
00:35:56,791 --> 00:35:57,791
- [chuckles]

815
00:35:57,875 --> 00:35:59,083
[snarls]

816
00:35:59,166 --> 00:36:00,708
Shamac!

817
00:36:00,791 --> 00:36:05,291
<i>♪ ♪</i>

818
00:36:05,375 --> 00:36:07,875
[shouting]

819
00:36:07,958 --> 00:36:11,958
<i>♪ ♪</i>

820
00:36:12,041 --> 00:36:13,208
I could do without the bugs,

821
00:36:13,291 --> 00:36:14,916
but I appreciate
the bacca fruit.

822
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,875
Thank you for that.
